Sentencas: The effective thickness or the active thickness of Ni-Sm-doped ceria cermet anode was investigated by measuring the performance of cells with different anode thickness.
Titulo: Effective thickness of Ni-Sm-doped ceria cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The performance of the solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) increased by increasing the anode thickness.
Titulo: Effective thickness of Ni-Sm-doped ceria cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The power density increased as the thickness increased and showed a maximum of 1 W/cm(2) at 2 A/cm(2) for 110 mu m anode.
Titulo: Effective thickness of Ni-Sm-doped ceria cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This large effective thickness of the electrode was most likely achieved due to the high sintering temperature.
Titulo: Effective thickness of Ni-Sm-doped ceria cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Although this structure may not be typical, it indicates an alternative method for the improvement of the anodic performance of SOFCs.
Titulo: Effective thickness of Ni-Sm-doped ceria cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cell
